lead_paragraph: The remarks by Lael Brainard, a proponent of continuing the Fed’s stimulus campaign, reinforce expectations that the Fed won’t raise rates this month.

headline.print_headline: Fed Official Continues Campaign for ‘Prudence’ in Increasing Rates
headline.main: Fed Official Says She Favors ‘Prudence’ in Raising Interest Rates

snippet: The remarks by Lael Brainard, a proponent of continuing the Fed’s stimulus campaign, reinforce expectations that the Fed won’t raise rates this month....
abstract: Federal Reserve governor Lael Brainard says she still supports 'prudence' in raising interest rates despite recent indications of economic growth; remarks bolster expectations Fed will not raise benchmark interest rate when committee meets in late September
